									domain
								</li>
								<ul>
									<li>
										ie: subsystem or a business process
									</li>
								</ul>
								<li>
									Establish loose relationships with other coarse graned components
								</li>
								<li>
									Often hide the implementation details defined by fine-grained components
								</li>
								<li>
									Usually has a differnet target audience
								</li>
							</ul>
